aa(lp56
VAnd it's funny \u2014 it feels a bit like this now for oil.
p57
aVWe've been spending the last few decades
p58
aVaccumulating a very powerful backlog of technologies
p59
aVfor saving and substituting for oil,
p60
aVand no one had bothered to add them up before.
p61
